General Electric Credit Corp, aunit of General Electric Co, said it has called for redemptionon April 13, 1987, its 150 mln dlrs 7-5/8 pct notes due 1988.    The company said the notes' redemption price is 100 pct oftheir principal amount plus accrued interest.    GE Credit said the Bank of New York will be theredemption's paying agent. Reuter&#3;